body:
OpenTelemetry metrics have been live for a while now and there have been no major bugs except the ongoing discussions around timers reporting in seconds or milliseconds ([example](https://github.com/apache/airflow/pull/39908)).  I propose we drop the "Experimental" banner for OTel Metrics and leave the new Experimental for OTel Traces.

@howardyoo 
@potiuk 
@romanzdk
@o-nikolas 

closes:  https://github.com/apache/airflow/discussions/40218
